---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Kristian Bjornebraten - Infrastructure Engineer, Cloud Architect, and DevOps enthusiast" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 720px;
				max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
				margin: auto;
				padding: 3em 1em;
			}
			.about-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			.about-avatar {
				width: 180px;
				height: 180px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				border: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.about-content {
				line-height: 1.8;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--color-text-main);
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				color: var(--color-text-main);
			}
			.tagline {
				color: var(--color-text-muted);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			h2 {
				margin-top: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				color: var(--color-accent);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			p {
				margin-bottom: 1.25em;
			}
			a {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			ul {
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
				padding-left: 1.5em;
			}
			li {
				margin-bottom: 0.75em;
			}
			strong {
				color: var(--color-text-main);
				font-weight: 600;
			}
			.highlight {
				background: var(--color-bg-alt);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			.tech-tags {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}
			.tech-tag {
				background: var(--color-bg-alt);
				color: var(--color-text-muted);
				padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
				border-radius: 20px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="about-header">
				<img src="/avatar.png" alt="Kristian Bjornebraten" class="about-avatar" />
				<h1>Kristian Bjornebraten</h1>
				<p class="tagline">Building cloud infrastructure and side projects from Norway</p>
			</div>

			<section class="about-content">
				<p>
					I have spent <strong>13 years in IT</strong>, most of them figuring out how to make infrastructure 
					less painful. These days I specialise in Azure, Terraform, and the kind of DevOps work that keeps 
					enterprise systems running without anyone noticing.
				</p>

				<div class="highlight">
					After hours, I put on headphones and build things for fun. Right now that means 
					<a href="https://tidwerk.com">TidWerk</a>, a time-tracking app for consultants, and 
					experimenting with <strong>MCP servers</strong> to see how AI agents can actually be useful 
					in a developer workflow. Yes, I am that kind of nerd.
				</div>

				<h2>The Day Job</h2>
				<p>
					I work as a consultant, usually wearing the hat of Technical Architect, Infrastructure Engineer, 
					or Delivery Manager depending on what the project needs. My focus is Azure: designing platforms, 
					writing Terraform, setting up CI/CD pipelines, and making sure things stay secure and compliant 
					without becoming a bureaucratic nightmare.
				</p>
				<p>
					I have worked in regulated industries like finance and healthcare where getting security wrong 
					is not an option. That taught me to think carefully about architecture decisions and document 
					the reasoning, not just the implementation.
				</p>

				<h2>Background</h2>
				<p>
					Over the years I have been a Tech Lead, Platform Engineer, IaC Developer, and Cloud Operator. 
					The common thread is infrastructure: building it, automating it, and helping teams work with it 
					effectively. I have led small teams, contributed to large platform projects, and spent more time 
					than I would like debugging networking issues between Azure and on-premises systems.
				</p>

				<h2>Tools I Reach For</h2>
				<div class="tech-tags">
					<span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Terraform</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Kubernetes</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">GitHub Actions</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Svelte</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Go</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">MCP Servers</span>
				</div>

				<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
				<p>
					Happy to talk about cloud architecture, DevOps, or whatever you are building. 
					Find me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bjornebraten/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a> 
					or check out what I am writing about on the <a href="/blog">blog</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
